StarWarsTable Question
Unique ID: SW-Table-001

You are building a small app that shows a list of Star Wars people in a table.

Input API
text
https://swapi.dev/api/people/?format=json
Response format (simplified)
json
[
{
"name": "Luke Skywalker",
"vehicles": ["https://swapi.dev/api/vehicles/14/", "..."],
"films": ["https://swapi.dev/api/films/1/", "..."]
}
]
Requirements
Fetch people list on component mount

Show loading spinner while main list loads

Render table with 3 columns: Name | Vehicles | Films

For each person row:

Name: direct name from person

Vehicles: call each vehicle URL → get name → join with ,

Films: call each film URL → get title → join with ,

Must handle:
Loading state for main list

Individual vehicle/film fetch errors (show "Unknown" for failed ones)

Don't crash if empty arrays
